    <title>Water contributor: Jim Lauria</title>
    <description>Jim Lauria is vice president of sales &amp;amp; marketing for Mazzei Injector Company, LLC, a fluid design company that manufactures mixing and contacting systems. He holds a Bachelor of Chemical Engineering degree from Manhattan College and has more than 20 years of global water treatment experience in the agricultural, municipal, industrial and commercial markets. Jim can be contacted at jlauria@mazzei.net.
 
